St._Cloud.Sartell High School:
Sartell High School is a public high school in Sartell, Minnesota. The school was constructed in 1993.


== Demographics ==
The demographic breakdown of the 1032 students enrolled for the 2012-2013 school year was:
Male - 52.5%
Female - 47.5%
Asian/Pacific islander - 1.3%
Black - 0.9%
Hispanic - 1.3%
White - 96.4%
Multiracial - 0.1%
In addition, 13.2% of the students were eligible for free or reduced lunch.
